name: Mediumship Reading
description: Whether attempting to contact a deceased loved one or receive divine guidance, Berry is available to interpret these messages for you. Through a variety of techniques and a host of guides, He can accurately and quickly transmit message from beyond - to you.

name: Meditation/Trance Assistance Session
description: Whether you have never meditated or entered a trance before and want to learn or you are a practiced veteran, Jenny can assist you in taking your trance and meditation even further. With a variety of tools and resources, she will offer you sound advice and training in a variety of meditative practices, depending on your needs. There is much to be learned in the art of trance and meditation, so additional sessions are offered at half the price of the initial session.

name: Astrological Chart
description: A fascinating and detailed report can be drawn up, indicating the position of the planets at your specific time of birth. Don't worry, if you don't know your time of birth, there is still a wealth of information to share with you regarding the position of the sun and moon as well as a few planets. The vibration of these planets had a profound effect on your perception. Any of the reports offered will cast a greater light on the vibrational energies that daily effect you.

name: Energy Scan/Healing
description: Energy operates on 3 levels - the emotional or mental, the spiritual and the physical. Negative stress often builds up in these areas and continues to grow over time. Without cleansing these energy fields, stress will continue to mount. Berry is available to scan and heal these systems. This may involve physical energy healing, chakra cleansing, aura patching or any number of techniques. To prevent further stress build, we highly recommend getting into the practice of yoga and meditation as these eliminate recent stress build up on the 3 energy systems.

name: Tarot or Crystal Ball Divination
description: Jenny is skilled and practiced in a variety of tarot and crystal ball readings. With a number of decks and layouts, she can provide a reading specific to your needs. As well, with her trusted and well loved crystal ball, she can scry messages from past, present and future.
